    <h1>AI Governance</h1>
    <p class="description">The set of rules, roles, and processes that manage how AI is built, deployed, monitored, and retired inside an organization. Gartner projects <strong>40% fewer AI compliance incidents</strong> by 2026 for companies with mature governance frameworks.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
